      "content": "it's that feeling that there's no point anymore. like, i've tried everything. the doctors, the pills, the therapy... nothing changes. it just feels like i'm just waiting for something to end. i keep thinking about how much easier it would be if everything was just... still. if i didn't have to feel anything at all.",
